58:39.848 --> 58:43.320
<i>People are buying more tickets,
T-shirts as souvenirs than ever.</i>

58:43.321 --> 58:45.791
<i>So if this is what we
the people are voting for,</i>

58:45.792 --> 58:48.362
<i>why did Congress
